#SecurityDomains
There are various ways to setup a security organisation. One way would be setup following deparments/domains 
Operations or Run Domains:
  Identity and Access Management
  Data Security 
  Application Security 
  Infrastructure and Network Security 
  Threat Management (Threat Hunting and Reasearch) 
  SOC 
  Governance, Risk and Compliance
Build or Change Functions: Program Management for each of about Domains
